thread.title: Deadly car wreck off California cliff may have been intentional

title: Deadly car wreck off California cliff may have been intentional
text:
Deadly car wreck off California cliff may have been intentional 9:06am EDT - 00:38 
Police say the SUV that plunged off a Northern California cliff into the Pacific Ocean last week, killing a family of eight, may have been driven off the coastal highway intentionally. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
